The MIT license above covers the code and text of this repository. Image
artifacts under runs/ (training samples, error heatmaps, worked-example
figures) are derivatives of open-licensed geodata and remain subject to
their sources' attribution terms, independent of the code license:

  © GeoBasis-DE/LGB, dl-de/by-2-0 (Brandenburg + Berlin orthophotos)
  © Bayerische Vermessungsverwaltung, CC BY 4.0 (Bavaria orthophotos)
  © HVBG Hessen, dl-de/by-2-0 (Hesse orthophotos)
  © Freie und Hansestadt Hamburg, LGV, dl-de/by-2-0 (Hamburg orthophotos)
